A simple CLI application to store and retrieve data from files.

Version:     0.1
Author:      Chris Kasza
Student ID:  100133723
Course:      COMP 3753
Assignment:  #1 - Data Storage Essentials

Usage:
kasza_a1 [DIR]

Where DIR is the path to the directory where the files will be stored.
If omitted /tmp/kasza_a1 will be used.


Supported commands:
ADD <name>; <email>; <year>; <country>
SHOW <attr> = <value>
SHOW <attr> > <value>
SHOW <attr> < <value>
DELETE <attr> = <value>
SET <attr> = <value> WHEN <attr2> = <value2>
QUIT


